trans-unit.source: Provides access to add attributes for one specific type to one specific <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 提供將一個特定類型的屬性新增至一個特定的存取<xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: The first time an <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> is queried for attributes for a type, if the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> was populated using <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> for that type, the delegate is passed a AttributeCallbackBuilder.
trans-unit.target: 第一次<xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>屬性進行查詢時對於類型，如果<xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder>使用填入<xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>該類型，傳遞給委派 AttributeCallbackBuilder。</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> removes the callback reference and adds any attribute information provided by calls to <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>移除回呼參考，並加入至<xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>。</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>呼叫所提供的任何屬性資訊</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>

trans-unit.source: Adds the contents of the provided attributes to the attribute table that created this builder.
trans-unit.target: 將提供之屬性的內容加入至建立此產生器的屬性表格。

trans-unit.source: If an attribute conflicts with another attribute already included in the table, the last attribute added replaces previous attributes.
trans-unit.target: 如果已經包含在資料表中的其他屬性的屬性與發生衝突，加入的最後一個屬性就會取代先前的屬性。

trans-unit.source: Attributes can be added only to the type specified by <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 屬性只能加入<xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder.CallbackType%2A>所指定的類型

trans-unit.source: The attributes that are added to the table.
trans-unit.target: 加入至資料表的屬性。

trans-unit.source: attributes is .
trans-unit.target: attributesis .
